Helpfile

A usable helpfile component with a fresh layout, that should look and feel good, cross-application, keyboard accessible

Pass the version number through the url

Dependencies: jQuery

Dual licensed under the MIT or GPL Version 2 licenses.

Author: dirkjan@degroot.in
Location: https://github.com/dirkjan111/helpfile
Version: 0.3
Date: 03-11-2011


V0.3 RELEASE NOTES (07-06-2013):

1) Noir/ high contrast theme for improved accessibility
2) Animated highlight section that show highlight markers
3) Keyboard accessibility of highlight markers - (CTRL-left or right arrow) - synchronized with highlights
4) Improved keyboard accessibility
5) Implemented Split screen, with possibility to maximize content window
6) Jshint compliance

